        <item>
            <title>黄仁勋到访台中夜市，被人潮所限空手而回</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/jensen-huang-taichung/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jensen-huang-taichung</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/jensen-huang-taichung/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 11:00:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NVIDIA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[台中]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黄仁勋]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287628</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NVIDIA 总裁黄仁勋对于台湾夜市情有独钟，之前曾现身台北的夜市，最近他首次造访台中，同样前往当地著名逢甲夜市，不过却遇到大批群组，场面混乱之下也无法继续行程。<br /><span id="more-1287628"></span></p><p>晚上黄仁勋原定前往逢甲夜市品尝美食，但因现场涌入大批粉丝，场面一度失控。短短 30 米的路程，他走了长达 40 分钟，最终为避免发生踩踏事故，不得不提前结束行程。有消息更指现场曾出现索取利是等不当行为，引起争议。</p><p>对于此次夜市行程受阻，黄仁勋幽默地回应指：「这次在台中逛夜市不要说吃了，连走进夜市都很难。」他期待未来能再次造访：「你们告诉我你们哪天不去，这样我就有机会去逛了！」对于总部选址台中的可能性，他以台语回应「当然有啊！」，并表示正在寻找合适的地点设立「非常漂亮的总部」。</p><p>黄仁勋此行除了访问矽品新厂外，还与台积电董事长魏哲家共进午餐，并出席纬创和 NVIDIA 的尾牙活动。他强调 NVIDIA 在台湾持续成长，需要更大的场地，欢迎各界提供合适的地点建议，展现 NVIDIA 深耕台湾市场的决心。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://today.line.me/tw/v2/article/9mWkp5g">太报</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/jensen-huang-taichung/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Casio 全新设计太阳能环保计数机，太阳能板放机顶提升美感</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/casio-comfy-jt-200t/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casio-comfy-jt-200t</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/18/casio-comfy-jt-200t/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 10:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gadgets]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CASIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[计数机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287568</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>信大家都曾经用过 Casio 计数机，有没有觉得其机面的太阳能板非常碍眼？为提升计数机美感，Casio 日本公司宣布本月将会推出全新太阳能计数机 Comfy JT-200T，售价为 3,850 日圆（约港币 193 元），全新设计的 Comfy JT-200T 特意将太阳能板放在机顶位置，一改以往置于机面之设计。Comfy JT-200T 以环保材料与经典设计为核心特色，集实用性与美学于一身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t00sc-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t00sc-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t00sc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden @container/thread"><div class="h-full"><div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-ybehe-79elbk h-full"><div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-ybehe-1n7m0yu"><div class="flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9"><article class="w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-21" data-scroll-anchor="true"><div class="m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5"><div class="mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2dc06602-410c-4008-acaa-78e3948eff36" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light"><p>Comfy JT-200T 的设计结合美观与实用性，将太阳能电池设置于机身顶部边缘，确保能源供应稳定，同时减少视觉干扰。这种设计提升产品整体简洁性，保持使用时计数机视觉清晰。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287581" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t031s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t031s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t031s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>机身提供五种柔和色调，包括米白、深灰、灰粉、灰绿及灰蓝，用户可随意挑选符合个人品味的颜色。外壳采用回收塑料制成，既提升耐用性，亦有效降低对环境的负担，展现了设计与实用的平衡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t048s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t048s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t048s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲共有 5 色可选，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t045s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t045s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t045s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用 59% 再生物料制成，图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>为纪念 Casio 首款计数机推出 60 周年，Comfy JT-200T 特别采用经典字体，赋予设计怀旧气息，同时融入现代美感。这款计数机配备 12 位 LCD 荧幕，画面清晰易读，功能简洁实用，并增设税务按钮，方便商务或个人用户轻松处理税率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t013s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t013s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t013s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287580" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t016s-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t016s-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/casioconfyjt200t016s.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/16/24345129/casio-japan-calculator-comfy-jt-200-design-solar-power-panel">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yGHR312sjU&amp;ab_channel=CASIOJapan">CASIO Japan@YouTube</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
